{"id":299570,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-副镇长带队逼迁，江苏如皋田书华被冷水/","date":"2013-06-18T05:48:50Z","modified":"2013-06-18T05:48:50Z","title":"维权网 | 副镇长带队逼迁，江苏如皋田书华被冷水浇头漏夜殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员肖微报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 9</span><span>月晚七点，如皋田书华向外发出求救信息，她家来了几十个不明身份的人，强行进入她的家里，半夜三更逼她和家人在空白合同上签字，后来认出带队的是如城镇的副镇长。田书华报警后，警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 065411</span><span>的警察出警，该警察看着她的手机被歹徒抢走，不仅不制止还一走了之，她和家人的生命财产由此受到严重威胁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>得到田书华的求救信息，南通网友王燕飞，张亮，高平，高凡菲等人立即驱车赶到如皋，和如皋褚开宏回合后前往如皋迎春派出所报案。谁知这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个人走出派出所时，遭到不明身份的人劫持并被打伤。网友们多次报警，据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/n/_____\">@<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">善<span lang=\"EN-US\">善若水耶</span></span></span></a></span><span>说：现在有好多网友在报案，但如皋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>平台女接线员分别为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>号，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>号，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>号，态度恶劣，不愿安排出警。再报警，如皋警察不作为，不调查，不了解，不救人。另据田书华的弟弟介绍，田书华本人，被打了一夜，还被冷水浇头，田书华妹妹及妹夫因要求见田书华也遭到毒打。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现场声援的朋友告诉本网信息员说：“种种迹象表明，王燕飞、张亮、朱磊三人被暴徒殴打，财物被抢。这是一起有预谋的警、官、匪勾结在一起的严重的刑事案件。我们控告如皋公安局警察不作为，强烈要求如皋政府给个说法，让犯罪分子受到应有的惩罚。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图片为王燕飞、张亮等人被打后的图片。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-k6JyqgY9akw/Ub-9RfFnnNI/AAAAAAAAjmQ/orqSe7J9Gok/s1600/IMG_3739.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-k6JyqgY9akw/Ub-9RfFnnNI/AAAAAAAAjmQ/orqSe7J9Gok/s320/IMG_3739.JPG\" width=\"191\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ewmErs61YyU/Ub-9RjqacaI/AAAAAAAAjmU/tb93k0IfNKY/s1600/IMG_3740.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ewmErs61YyU/Ub-9RjqacaI/AAAAAAAAjmU/tb93k0IfNKY/s320/IMG_3740.JPG\" width=\"191\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_aINwYZzJeQ/Ub-9TiTIqYI/AAAAAAAAjmg/vF3t4QfnvfA/s1600/IMG_3744.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_aINwYZzJeQ/Ub-9TiTIqYI/AAAAAAAAjmg/vF3t4QfnvfA/s320/IMG_3744.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}